{"tid":199625,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戴頭盔-美聯航今日乘客","createTime":"2017-04-13T10:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T07:56:52.000Z","uid":75299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1f90a9ccd0b2a3afc72f48bccaeb5900fadca79","tid":199625,"uid":75299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T10:32:02.000Z","msg":"聯航事件後 乘客戴頭盔登機 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBzMXb2.img?h=410&amp;w=728&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=920&amp;y=613\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBzMXb2.img%3Fh%3D410%26w%3D728%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D920%26y%3D613&h=862e5209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國聯合航空強拖乘客離機事件曝光後，迅速成為全球輿論熱點，更有對事件進行網友惡搞。<br />\n<br />\n雖然，聯航發表聲明再次道歉，表示將「負全部責任」，但許多民眾開始擔心，自己是否會有一天遭受同樣的對待。<br />\n<br />\n於是有網友在微博分享了一張題為「美聯航今日乘客」的照片，雖然只是惡搞，但應景的照片還是引來大批網友的圍觀和點贊。圖中的場景為某架飛機的內艙，而機上的大部分乘客都戴上了頭盔，只有個別乘客沒有戴。<br />\n<br />\n戴了頭盔的乘客在美聯航的客機上泰然自若的坐著，相比之下，沒戴頭盔的乘客只能在角落裡瑟瑟發抖。<br />\n<br />\n惡搞照片引來大量網友點讚，然而事實上，圖中場景是德國神鷹航空（Condor Flugdienst）的機艙。"},{"pid":"aa1851ddf1347fe59e67aaae23c7f76559bdbe25","tid":199625,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T10:33:48.000Z","msg":"比串到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc33e6f144c293497eac174bd0845eb5fc2222e","tid":199625,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64788abfa875456139dc39c244b342dd99567c94","tid":199625,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:31:13.000Z","msg":"沒戴頭盔的乘客只能在角落裡瑟瑟發抖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5331ee69d379e810670c628363db82b5ed67aba2","tid":199625,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T07:56:52